{
  "title": "基础 WHERE 子句",
  "group": "SQL 基础",
  "options": [
    {
      "text": "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name LIKE(John);"
    },
    {
      "text": "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = 'John';"
    },
    {
      "text": "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name == \"John\";"
    },
    {
      "text": "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name === \"John\";"
    }
  ],
  "objectives": [],
  "questionProse": [
    "下列哪个 SQL 查询能正确检索出 name 为 \"John\" 的行？"
  ],
  "hintsProse": [],
  "explanationProse": [
    "在 SQL 中，`WHERE` 子句使用单个等号 (`=`) 进行等值检查，而不是 JavaScript 中使用的 `==` 或 `===` 运算符。\n\n正确的语法是 `SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = 'John';`。"
  ]
}
